ìjápọ̀ yìí.','Enter custom alt text for the linked keywords. This is only used if "Custom Text" is selected above.'=>'Tẹ ọrọ alt aṣa fun awọn ọrọ-ọrọ ti a so pọ. Eyi ni a lo nikan ti "Ọrọ Aṣa" ba ti yan loke.','Post Types'=>'Ìru Ìwé','Where should these keywords be auto-linked?'=>'Níbo ni àwọn kókó-ọrọ yìí yẹ kí a jápọ̀ àtọka?','Auto-linking'=>'Ìjápọ̀-àtọka','Redirection'=>'Ìtẹ̀síwájú','Redirection Method'=>'Ọna Ìtẹ̀síwájú','Select redirection method'=>'Yan ọ̀nà ìtẹ̀síwájú','Select a method'=>'Yan ọ̀nà kan','Mark links as sponsored content.'=>'Ṣàkóso àwọn ìjápọ gẹ́gẹ́ bí akoonu ìpolówó.','Adds rel="sponsored" attribute. Recommended for affiliate links and paid promotions.'=>'Fi àdírẹsì rel="ìpolówó" kun. A ṣe iṣeduro fún àwọn ìjápọ alafaramo àti àwọn ìpolówó tí a san.','Prevent search engines from following this link.'=>'Dènà àwọn ẹrọ ìwádìí láti tẹ̀lé ìjápọ yìí.','Adds rel="nofollow" attribute. Recommended for external links and untrusted sources.'=>'Fi àdírẹsì rel="nofollow" kun. A ṣe iṣeduro fún àwọn ìjápọ àtọka àti àwọn orísun tí a kò gbẹ́kẹ̀ lé.','Pass URL parameters to the target link.'=>'Fẹ́ ẹ̀ka URL sí ìjápọ àfojúsùn.','Any parameters added to the short URL (e.g., ?utm_source=email) will be forwarded to the target URL.'=>'Gbogbo àwọn párámetà tí a fi kun sí URL kukuru (àpẹẹrẹ: ?utm_source=email) yóò jẹ́ kí a fi ranṣẹ́ sí URL àfojúsùn.','Password Protection'=>'Ìdánilójú Ọrọ aṣínà','Secure your shortlink.'=>'Dáàbò bo ìjápọ kukuru rẹ.','Users must enter the password to redirect to the target link.'=>'Àwọn olumulo gbọdọ̀ tẹ ọrọ aṣínà wọlé láti tún ìjápọ àfojúsùn.','Password'=>'Ọrọ aṣínà','Share this with users.'=>'Pín ìyẹn pẹ̀lú àwọn olumulo.','Passwords are case sensitive.'=>'Àwọn ọrọ aṣínà jẹ́ ìmọ̀lára ọ̀rọ.','********'=>'********','Enable Expiration'=>'Mú Ìparí ṣiṣẹ́','Set an expiration date and time for shortlinks.'=>'Ṣeto ọjọ ipari ati akoko fun awọn ọna asopọ kukuru.','After the expiration date and time pass, visitors will no longer be able to access the shortlink.'=>'Lẹhin ti ọjọ ipari ati akoko ba kọja, awọn alejo ko ni ni anfani lati wọle si ọna asopọ kukuru naa.','Select the date when this shortlink should stop working.'=>'Yan ọjọ ti ọna asopọ kukuru yii yẹ ki o da working duro.','Select the time when the shortlink should expire.'=>'Yan akoko ti ọna asopọ kukuru yẹ ki o parẹ.','Must be at least 1 minute in the future. Combined with the date above to set the exact expiration moment.'=>'O gbọdọ jẹ o kere ju iṣẹju 1 ni ọjọ iwaju. Papọ pẹlu ọjọ loke lati ṣeto akoko ipari gangan.','Security'=>'Aabo','Analytics'=>'Itupalẹ','Post not found.'=>'Ifiweranṣẹ ko ri.','This post is in {status} status. It is not visible to the public.'=>'Ipò ìfiranṣẹ yi wa ni ipo {status}. Kii ṣe kedere si gbogbo eniyan.','This link has expired'=>'Ọna asopọ yii ti pari','You will be redirected shortly.'=>'Iwọ yoo yipada laipẹ.','Click here if you are not redirected'=>'Tẹ nibi ti o ko ba yipada','Link Expired'=>'Ọna asopọ ti pari','This link is not active.'=>'Ọna asopọ yii ko ṣiṣẹ.','This link is expired.'=>'Ọna asopọ yii ti pari.','Incorrect password. Please try again.'=>'Ọrọigbaniwọle ti ko tọ. Jọwọ gbiyanju lẹẹkansi.','Password Protected Link'=>'Ọna asopọ ti o ni aabo pẹlu ọrọigbaniwọle','Enter password to continue:'=>'Tẹ ọrọigbaniwọle lati tẹsiwaju:','Submit'=>'Firanṣẹ','This link is not containing the right prefix slug.'=>'Ọna asopọ yii ko ni prefix slug to tọ.','Too many invalid shortlink requests. Please try again later.'=>'Ọpọ awọn ibeere ọna asopọ kukuru ti ko tọ. Jọwọ gbiyanju lẹẹkansi nigbamii.','Too Many Requests'=>'Ọpọ Awọn ibeere','Invalid revision ID.'=>'ID atunṣe ti ko wulo.','Draft'=>'Iwe afọwọkọ','Pending Review'=>'N duro de Atunwo','Private'=>'Ikọkọ','Customize the notice shown for each enabled non-published status. Available placeholders: {status}, {date}, {title}.'=>'Ṣatunkọ akiyesi ti a fihan fun ọkọọkan ipo ti ko ti kọja. Awọn aaye ti o wa: {status}, {date}, {title}.','Settings'=>'Eto','Select which post statuses are accessible when visiting a PublishPress shortlink.'=>'Yan iru ipo ifiweranṣẹ wo ni a le wọle si nigba ti a ba ṣabẹwo si ọna asopọ kukuru PublishPress.','PublishPress Statuses Plugin Detected:'=>'Aami Ipo PublishPress ti wa ni awari:','To use core PublishPress statuses with Shortlinks, Please enable the Shortlinks post type in PublishPress Statuses workflow settings.'=>'Lati lo awọn ipo PublishPress ipilẹ pẹlu Awọn ọna asopọ Kukuru, Jọwọ mu iru ifiweranṣẹ Awọn ọna asopọ Kukuru ṣiṣẹ ni awọn eto ṣiṣe iṣẹ Ipo PublishPress.','Elementor Detected:'=>'Elementor ti wa ni awari:','Shortlink prefix is required for proper rendering of Elementor revisions. It is advisable to keep it enabled.'=>'A nilo prefix ọna asopọ kukuru fun itọju to pe ti awọn atunṣe Elementor. O jẹ imọran lati tọju rẹ ni mu.','TinyPress Shortlinks Notice:'=>'Ikilọ Ọna asopọ Kukuru TinyPress:','Elementor is active. Shortlink prefix has been automatically disabled, it is required for optimal compatibility with Elementor revisions.'=>'Elementor n ṣiṣẹ. Prefix ọna asopọ kukuru ti wa ni pipa laifọwọyi, o nilo fun ibamu to dara julọ pẹlu awọn atunṣe Elementor.','Published'=>'Ti a tẹjade','Shortlink Prefix'=>'Prefix Ọna asopọ Kukuru','Add a prefix between your domain name and shortlink.'=>'Fi prefix kan kun laarin orukọ agbegbe rẹ ati ọna asopọ kukuru.','Prefix Slug'=>'Prefix Slug','Custom prefix slug.'=>'Slug prefix aṣa.','This text will be added between your domain name and shortlink.'=>'Iwe afọwọkọ yii yoo wa ni afikun laarin orukọ agbegbe rẹ ati ọna asopọ kukuru.','go'=>'lọ','Keyboard Shortcut'=>'Kíkó Bọtini','Create shortlinks from anywhere inside your WordPress dashboard.'=>'Ṣẹda awọn ọna asopọ kukuru lati ibi eyikeyi ninu dashboard WordPress rẹ.','Ctrl or Cmd + /'=>'Ctrl tabi Cmd + /','Remove from Admin Bar'=>'Yọ kuro ni Bar Admin','Hide the "Shorten" button from the WordPress admin bar.'=>'Tọju bọtini "Dínkù" kuro ni bar admin WordPress.','Role Management'=>'Iṣakoso Ipa','Who Can View Shortlinks'=>'Tani Le Wo Awọn Kèkèké Línkì','Only selected user roles can view links.'=>'Awọn ipa olumulo ti a yan nikan ni wọn le wo awọn ọna asopọ.','Who Can Create/Edit Shortlinks'=>'Tani Le Ṣẹda/Edit Awọn Kèkèké Línkì','Only selected user roles can create or edit links.'=>'Awọn ipa olumulo ti a yan nikan ni wọn le ṣẹda tabi ṣe atunṣe awọn ọna asopọ.','Who Can See Analytics'=>'Tani Le Ri Awọn Iṣiro','Only selected user roles can see analytics.'=>'Awọn ipa olumulo ti a yan nikan ni wọn le ri awọn iṣiro.','Who Can Control Settings'=>'Tani Le Ṣakoso Eto','Only selected user roles can control settings.'=>'Awọn ipa olumulo ti a yan nikan ni wọn le ṣakoso awọn eto.','Auto-Linking'=>'Akọsílẹ-Auto','Enable Auto-Linking'=>'Mú Akọsílẹ-Auto ṣiṣẹ','Automatically convert keywords to shortlinks in post content.'=>'Yipada awọn bọtini ọrọ si awọn ọna asopọ kekeke laifọwọyi ninu akoonu ifiweranṣẹ.','When enabled, keywords configured in shortlink settings will be automatically linked in your content.'=>'Nigbati a ba mu ṣiṣẹ, awọn bọtini ọrọ ti a ṣeto ninu awọn eto ọna asopọ kekeke yoo jẹ asopọ laifọwọyi ninu akoonu rẹ.','Open Auto-Links In'=>'Ṣii Awọn Aso-Akọsílẹ Ni','Choose how auto-linked keywords should open.'=>'Yan bi awọn bọtini ọrọ ti a so pọ yẹ ki o ṣii.','Same tab'=>'Tẹ́ńbá àtàwọn','New tab'=>'Tẹ́ńbá tuntun','Auto-Link Color'=>'Àwọ̀ Akọsílẹ-Auto','Choose the color for auto-linked keywords.'=>'Yan awọ fun awọn bọtini ọrọ ti a so pọ.','Auto-List Links'=>'Akọsílẹ-Auto Línkì','Auto-List Shortlinks'=>'Akọsílẹ-Auto Kekèké Línkì','When enabled, shortlinks will appear in the "All Links" table based on the behavior you configure below.'=>'Nigbati o ba ti mu ṣiṣẹ, awọn ọna asopọ kukuru yoo han ninu tabili "Gbogbo Awọn ọna asopọ" da lori ihuwasi ti o ṣeto ni isalẹ.','Configure Post Types'=>'Configure Post Types','Set when links should be auto-listed for each post type'=>'Ṣeto nigbati awọn ọna asopọ yẹ ki o wa ni akojọ laifọwọyi fun ọkọọkan post type','Add post types and configure when their shortlinks should appear in the "All Links" table. Changes are saved automatically.'=>'Fikun un post types ki o si ṣeto nigbati awọn ọna asopọ kukuru wọn yẹ ki o han ninu tabili "Gbogbo Awọn ọna asopọ". Awọn ayipada ni a fipamọ laifọwọyi.','Post Status Visibility'=>'Post Status Visibility','Allowed Post Statuses'=>'Allowed Post Statuses','Unpublished Content Notice'=>'Iwe Ikilọ Akopọ Ti Ko Ti Kọja','Show a frontend notice when an internal shortlink displays a post that is not published.'=>'Fihan akiyesi ni iwaju nigbati ọna asopọ inu ba n ṣafihan ifiweranṣẹ ti ko ti kọja.','Notice Post Statuses'=>'Awọn ipo Ifiweranṣẹ Ikilọ','This notice only applies to internal shortlinks that render post content directly. External shortlinks are not affected.'=>'Iwe ikilọ yii kan si awọn ọna asopọ inu nikan ti o n ṣe afihan akoonu ifiweranṣẹ taara. Awọn ọna asopọ ita ko ni ipa.','Notice Messages'=>'Awọn ifiranṣẹ Ikilọ','Default redirection method for shortlinks'=>'Ọna atunṣe aiyipada fun awọn ọna asopọ kukuru','Mark links as sponsored content'=>'Samisi awọn ọna asopọ gẹgẹbi akoonu ti a ṣe atilẹyin','Prevent search engines from following links'=>'Dena awọn ẹrọ iṣawari lati tẹle awọn ọna asopọ','Pass URL parameters to target links'=>'Gbe awọn paramita URL si awọn ọna asopọ afojusun','Secure your shortlinks'=>'Ṣe aabo awọn ọna asopọ kukuru rẹ','Users must enter a password to redirect to the target link.'=>'Awọn olumulo gbọdọ tẹ ọrọ igbaniwọle kan lati yipada si ọna asopọ ti a fojusi.','Default Password'=>'Ọrọ igbaniwọle aiyipada','Default password for protected links'=>'Ọrọ igbaniwọle aiyipada fun awọn ọna asopọ ti a daabobo','This password will be used for links that have password protection enabled via global settings. Passwords are case sensitive.'=>'Ọrọ igbaniwọle yii yoo ṣee lo fun awọn ọna asopọ ti o ni aabo pẹlu ọrọ igbaniwọle ti a mu ṣiṣẹ nipasẹ awọn eto kariaye. Awọn ọrọ igbaniwọle jẹ ẹtọ si ọran.','Set an expiration date and time for shortlinks'=>'Ṣeto ọjọ ati akoko ipari fun awọn ọna asopọ kukuru','Select the date when this shortlink should stop working'=>'Yan ọjọ ti ọna asopọ kukuru yii yẹ ki o da ṣiṣẹ','Select the time when the shortlink should expire'=>'Yan akoko ti ọna asopọ kukuru yẹ ki o pari','Revisions'=>'Revisions','Revision Link Visibility'=>'Ihuwasi Asọye Atunṣe','When enabled, revision shortlinks will appear in the "All Shortlinks" table based on the behavior you configure below.'=>'Nigbati o ba ti mu ṣiṣẹ, awọn ọna asopọ kukuru atunṣe yoo han ninu tabili "Gbogbo Awọn ọna asopọ kukuru" da lori ihuwasi ti o ṣeto ni isalẹ.','When Revision is Created'=>'Nigbati Atunṣe ba ti ṣẹda','When Revision is Created or Link is First Used'=>'Nigbati Atunṣe ba ti ṣẹda tabi ọna asopọ ti wa ni lilo akọkọ','Show Shortlink in Revision Table'=>'Fihan Shortlink ninu Iwe Atunyẹwo','Display shortlink column when viewing revisions in PublishPress Revisions.'=>'Fihan àkọsílẹ shortlink nigba ti o n wo awọn atunṣe ni PublishPress Revisions.','Revision Visibility for Visitors'=>'Ifarahan Atunyẹwo fun Awọn Alejo','Allow logged-out visitors to view revision content via shortlinks.'=>'Jẹ ki awọn alejo ti ko wọlé wo akoonu atunṣe nipasẹ shortlinks.','By default, PublishPress Revisions blocks visitors from viewing revision previews. When enabled, revision shortlinks will render the revision content directly for logged-out visitors instead of redirecting to the preview URL.'=>'Ni aiyipada, PublishPress Revisions dènà awọn alejo lati wo awọn ayẹwo atunṣe. Nigba ti a ba mu un ṣiṣẹ, awọn shortlinks atunṣe yoo ṣe afihan akoonu atunṣe taara fun awọn alejo ti ko wọlé dipo ti yí wọn lọ si URL ayẹwo.','Dummy'=>'Dummy','No post types configured yet. Click "Add Post Type" to get started.'=>'Ko si awọn iru post ti a ti ṣeto sibẹsibẹ. Tẹ "Fi Iru Post Kún" lati bẹrẹ.','Add Post Type'=>'Fi Iru Post Kún','Log entry deleted successfully.'=>'Iwé àkọọlẹ ti pa ni aṣeyọri.','%d log entries deleted successfully.'=>'%d iwe àkọọlẹ ti pa ni aṣeyọri.','All logs have been cleared.'=>'Gbogbo awọn iwe àkọọlẹ ti wa ni mimọ.','Title'=>'Àkọlé','Details'=>'Àlàyé','Are you sure you want to delete this log entry?'=>'Ṣe o dájú pe o fẹ pa iwe àkọọlẹ yii?','Tablet'=>'Tablet','Mobile'=>'Mobile','Desktop'=>'Desktop','%1$s from %2$s visited at %3$s'=>'%1$s lati %2$s ṣabẹwo ni %3$s','%1$s visited at %2$s'=>'%1$s ṣabẹwo ni %2$s','From %1$s, visited at %2$s'=>'Lati %1$s, ṣabẹwo ni %2$s','Visited at %s'=>'Ti a ṣàbẹwò ni %s','via %s'=>'nipasẹ %s','Edit shortlink settings'=>'Ṣatunkọ eto asopọ kukuru','This post is in {status} status. It will become visible to the public on {date}.'=>'Iwe ifiweranṣẹ yii wa ni ipo {status}. Yoo di mimọ si gbogbo eniyan ni {date}.','Target url not found.'=>'URL ibi ti a ń fẹ ko ri.','Invalid URL scheme. Only http, https, ftp, ftps, and mailto are allowed.'=>'Ilana URL ti ko tọ. Nikan http, https, ftp, ftps, ati mailto ni a gba laaye.','Tiny slug could not created.'=>'A ko le ṣẹda slug kekere.','Shortlink will appear here'=>'Asopọ kukuru yoo han nibi','Enter a long URL and make a shortlink'=>'Tẹ URL gigun kan ki o ṣẹda asopọ kukuru','Long URL'=>'URL Gigun','Create Shortlink'=>'Ṣẹda Asopọ Kukuru','Reset Today\'s Analytics'=>'Tun Analytics Ọjọ́ Tó Rẹ́ Sọ́kan','Reset Week\'s Analytics'=>'Tun Analytics Ọsẹ́ Tó Rẹ́ Sọ́kan','Reset Month\'s Analytics'=>'Tun Analytics Oṣù Tó Rẹ́ Sọ́kan','Reset Year\'s Analytics'=>'Tun Analytics Ọdún Tó Rẹ́ Sọ́kan','Are you sure you want to reset the analytics for this period? This action cannot be undone.'=>'Ṣé o dájú pé o fẹ́ tun awọn analytics fun akoko yii? Iṣe yii ko le pada sẹhin.','Today'=>'Loni','Last 7 Days'=>'Ọjọ́ 7 Tó Kẹhin','Last 1 Month'=>'Oṣù 1 to kẹhin','Last 1 Year'=>'Ọdún 1 to kẹhin','If you like %1$s please leave us a %2$s rating. Thank you!'=>'Ti o ba fẹ %1$s jọwọ fi wa %2$s ìdíyelé. Ẹ ṣé!','About'=>'Nipa','Documentation'=>'Iwe aṣẹ','Contact'=>'Kan si','Download QR Code'=>'Gba Koodu QR','We have developed extensions for the below browsers.'=>'A ti ṣe idagbasoke awọn afikun fun awọn aṣawakiri ti o wa ni isalẹ.','Click on your preferred one to Download the extension.'=>'Tẹ lori ọkan ti o fẹ lati Gba afikun naa.','Download the Extension'=>'Gba afikun naa','Need PublishPress Shortlinks Support?'=>'Nilo Atilẹyin PublishPress Shortlinks?','If you need help or have a new feature request, let us know.'=>'Ti o ba nilo iranlọwọ tabi ni ibeere ẹya tuntun, jẹ ki a mọ.','Request Support'=>'Beere Atilẹyin','Detailed documentation is also available on the plugin website.'=>'Iwe aṣẹ alaye tun wa lori oju opo wẹẹbu plugin naa.','View Knowledge Base'=>'Wo Ibi ìmọ','This plugin can be deleted.'=>'A le pa plugin yii run.','Copied.'=>'Ti a daakọ.']];